csdn.net/ma123rui/article/details/104704831","line":72},{"title":"2","target":"https://zhidao.baidu.com/question/389787422.html","line":72},{"title":"驻点","target":"../../../驻点.md","line":74},{"title":"拐点：拐点是函数凹凸性发生变化的点。在拐点处，函数的二阶导数发生变号。如果函数的二阶导数在某点从正变为负，或从负变为正，那么该点就是拐点。拐点通常对应函数图像的弯曲变化3","target":"https://www.cnblogs.com/wmzh/p/15516275.html","line":77},{"title":"概念 ","target":"../../../概念.md","line":84},{"title":"开区间","target":"../../../开区间.md","line":84},{"title":"导数及其应用","target":"../../../选修二/Highlights/Page 008/导数及其应用.md","line":85},{"title":"极限","target":"../../../极限.md","line":88},{"title":"２ 导数的几何意义","target":"../../../选修二/Highlights/Page 012/２ 导数的几何意义.md","line":89},{"title":"割线","target":"../../../割线.md","line":90},{"title":"驻点","target":"../../../驻点.md","line":92},{"title":"导函数","target":"../../../导函数.md","line":94},{"title":"基本初等函数框架","target":"../../../chengbai高中数学框架(承白","line":95},{"title":"常数函数、幂函 数、指数函数、对数函 数、三角函数、反三角 函数被称为基本初等 函数．","target":"../../../选修二/Highlights/Page 018/常数函数、幂函 数、指数函数、对数函 数、三角函数、反三角 函数被称为基本初等 函数．.md","line":96},{"title":"复合函数","target":"../../../复合函数.md","line":102},{"title":"https://remnote-user-data.s3.amazonaws.com/1ZZjTB9dkmrGfrlcgHEHTD_7ve_Fh1DU9MMjNuzdMOAxILx8Fkm3a2HAkxKFtc0ZpNR5wIgJJxL8AlflRwbdM0iWA7rBOf518wBiTeSo7Yds2zX1cbif8v6R9ifKy_oh.png","target":"../../../选修二/Highlights/Page 015/Untitled.md","line":105},{"title":"利用导数研究函数的单调性","target":"../../../选修二/Highlights/第 026 页/利用导数研究函数的单调性.md","line":106},{"title":"定理","target":"../../../定理.md","line":107},{"title":"极值点","target":"../../../极值点.md","line":112},{"title":"https://remnote-user-data.s3.amazonaws.com/I2hpP1U2czuepCA0cgvQJWRvXAMILgxQQpCtqDDfOKceHhjsYkH7iopACE-T42wUuHIlXrKsXf4syiL8ihyyTxvirh4TTXPFAnn9V1T25keDilgnnZ-46k6ECnhEfmjN.png","target":"../../../选修二/Highlights/Page 029/Untitled.md","line":112},{"title":"必要性探路","target":"../../../必要性/必要性探路.md","line":136},{"title":"定理","target":"../../../定理.md","line":140},{"title":"驻点","target":"../../../驻点.md","line":142},{"t